            "title": "港股開跌65點   電動車及光伏股回落  阿里續升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數開跌65點或0.24%，報27221 ; 恒生科技指數開跌29點或0.44%，報6653 ; 恒生國企指數報9693，跌30點或0.31%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交28.26億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)升1.04%，報185元，成交居首。百度(09888)跌1.37%，報137.3元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">東風(00489)升1.31%，報9.25元，分拆嵐圖介紹上市。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比亞迪(01211)跌1.49%，報112.2元; 理想汽車(02015)跌1.37%報100.6元 ; 小鵬(09868)月月銷售破紀錄，惟股價開跌2.36%，報92.8元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">寧德時代(03750)挫1.65%，報595.5元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">光伏股回落，福耀玻璃(03606)挫1.68%，報76.2元; 信義光能(00968)跌0.27%，報3.77元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紫金黃金國際(02259)升1.09%，報139元。</p>\n</div>",
